WEBVTT


00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:02.669
If you travel to Europe now in two thousand and twenty-four, 

00:00:02.669 --> 00:00:03.920
avoid making these mistakes. 

00:00:04.360 --> 00:00:06.931
From February you must demonstrate that you are worth 

00:00:06.931 --> 00:00:09.360
one hundred and thirteen euros a day to stay here. 

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:12.498
If the police ask you to demonstrate this and you don't, 

00:00:12.498 --> 00:00:14.400
they may not let you into the country. 

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:15.769
If you travel with Ryan, 

00:00:15.769 --> 00:00:18.194
you are and your flight is bought by an agency 

00:00:18.194 --> 00:00:19.999
that is not the company's website, 

00:00:19.999 --> 00:00:22.579
avoid checking in directly at the airport because 

00:00:22.579 --> 00:00:24.591
they can charge you up to fifty euros, 

00:00:24.591 --> 00:00:27.376
so always try to check in through the website itself. 

00:00:27.376 --> 00:00:27.841
the app. 

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:29.405
From the twenty-fifth of April, 

00:00:29.405 --> 00:00:31.075
if you are going to travel to Venice, 

00:00:31.075 --> 00:00:33.667
already prepare your pocket and now they will charge a five

00:00:33.667 --> 00:00:35.600
-euro entrance fee to get to know the city. 

00:00:35.720 --> 00:00:36.908
If you don't buy tickets, 

00:00:36.908 --> 00:00:38.920
you can be fined up to three hundred euros. 

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:41.944
To enter the Colosseum you must bring a document, 

00:00:41.944 --> 00:00:43.546
as now the entries are Nominal, 

00:00:43.546 --> 00:00:45.600
they will take your first and last name. 

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:47.235
If you have no document, 

00:00:47.235 --> 00:00:50.680
they may not let you enter the Colosseum and end your trip. 

